				<td colspan="2"><span>Sinfonian, I've been meaning to ask other bards what they do on Takish LDoN missions. <b>THE DOORS ARE KILLING ME!</b> Lately, what I've been doing is using my singing steel helm to target mobs directly inside of the doors, but that's a good 1 minute+ wasted on lulling. Other than spending about 100p+ to invest in stalking probes, has anybody found something that would be more time effective? I really want to get up to some Royal Attendant Armor, but alot of the time my missions are <b>REALLY</b> close to failing, if not failed.</span></td>
