				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: OMG Bards are POWERFUL in LDoN!<a name="12910"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 5 03 9:17 PM</span></td>
