				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: OMG Bards are POWERFUL in LDoN!<a name="13118"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 11 03 4:50 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah F9 is our savior for Takish.  It doesn't slow anything up, and you only need to hit the one in front of you, and the two that are there to ambush us.  With those three lulled, usually I don't need to hit the rest of the room until I am done pulling the two by the door.  By then, I have plenty of room to go back and get the rest of the room.  My song line up:
<br />

<br />
1.) Largo's (Snare or pull depending on how I have the group timed.)
<br />
2.) Replenishment (I can't wait for marr)
<br />
3.) Psalm of Purity (DS - can't wait for Veeshan)
<br />
4.) Rondo's (DS and Haste if needed)
<br />
5.) Warsong (Overhaste)
<br />
6.) Ayonae (I want Terris as this one is almost useless now)
<br />
7.) Assonance (Fast pulls and dot, largo's for slow pulls)
<br />
8.) Quellious (Ahh about time) =)</span></td>
