				<td colspan="2"><span>Another way to get around the doors is to open it and stand in the middle.  I usually Quellious the ones I can see until the door closes with me in the middle.  Once it is closed I can look from side to side with little chance of aggro.  I Quellious one of them and pull the other.
<br />

<br />
Wait til you get Fading Memories, Sinfonian.  The bard's get out of death free card<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />  It is very nice in a dungeon when you get a couple from around the corner that added.
